<br />\n<br />\n一定要為佢打氣，畀信心佢！加油吖！<br />\n有唔明可以問我吖，樂意解答～ <br />\n我tg：muichumama <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:33:21.000Z","msg":"同你好似，佢又係脾氣好差，佢唔肯食真係無人迫到。雲芝，黑酵母我都有買，但佢食唔夠一半就開始無曬食慾了，所以我都餵唔到。。唉。其實佢好辛苦既話我寧願佢訓住走，唔想佢受咁多苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瘦到皮包骨。btw多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得依加處於人生低谷，好難過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"餵唔到都要諗方法餵吖，我嗰時係用蜜糖溝雲芝蟲草嘅粉（拆開膠囊），撈完當醬查麵包畀佢，後期佢嗰食麵包，鍾意食潔齒骨，我就用潔齒骨「了」啲藥醬畀佢... <br />\n<br />\n嗰時呀女都好瘦好瘦，走嗰時得14.4kg，明明最高峰係21kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話kakato嘅杞子雞罐罐好香，佢哋鍾意食，你可以試吓<br />\n嗰時我個女鍾意食be my baby嘅罐罐"},{"pid":"a41c90b2b7ed759fcb53355fcf4931cb70d7f817","tid":1674370,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"樓主你一定要陪佢多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b15b9dcf27a2a9a9e61674ab27e3d17683b5d2","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf52753c3309df1161431334d19a634ec68e3692","tid":1674370,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9744b89f29554bab4d509508e34211db629626c0","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score