<br />\n食唔到野<br />\n明明知道肚餓<br />\n開好多好多唔同既糧比佢都係聞下當食左<br />\n食少少又嘔多多<br />\n望住佢自己咩都做唔到真係好難受<br />\n<br />\n好想知道佢諗咩<br />\n係咪痛<br />\n定想靜下<br />\n定想有人陪<br />\n定有啲咩心願<br />\n<br />\n貓貓最後去左彩虹橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzsupZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzsupZD.png&h=bcd44d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信狗狗最需要係你既陪伴"},{"pid":"78721cc5fd926a4e109976d88c00a0eada58bcc1","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6136b6312dde599d579428789ae068ecc7f05af","tid":1674370,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5dc078b56ce983ff1c1bb76bdac84f13eefb410","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a41c90b2b7ed759fcb53355fcf4931cb70d7f817","tid":1674370,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"樓主你一定要陪佢多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"我都想唔洗番工全天候係佢身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一出門我都好不安"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"咁唯有盡力放左工就仆返屋企陪佢啦多d摸下佢錫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前就係放左學掛住補習 結果咁啱個日補耐左 返到屋企就已經見唔到我隻狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"一諗到將來佢只會存在係我既記憶，我就傷心到死，要好好記得觸摸佢既感覺，佢既氣味"},{"pid":"f9d8f99ea9cf04a3d941b2d81fc4c3a389744a78","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ebeabc41c2cb7614cfa4b91644a903b9932d4a6","tid":1674370,"uid":321724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"我貓貓8月都係腸有事<br />\n3k幾暴瘦到唔夠2k<br />\n佢係橘貓明明圓碌碌變到皮包骨<br />\n行唔到直線<br />\n腳仔都拎唔起<br />\n但係好乖<br />\n見到人番屋企會叫你雖然好細聲<br />\n無氣無力都會走入砂盆去廁所<br />\n<br />\n食唔到野<br />\n明明知道肚餓<br />\n開好多好多唔同既糧比佢都係聞下當食左<br />\n食少少又嘔多多<br />\n望住佢自己咩都做唔到真係好難受<br />\n<br />\n好想知道佢諗咩<br />\n係咪痛<br />\n定想靜下<br />\n定想有人陪<br />\n定有啲咩心願<br />\n<br />\n貓貓最後去左彩虹橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzsupZD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzsupZD.png&h=bcd44d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信狗狗最需要係你既陪伴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"見住佢瘦同虛弱真係好無助，呢種痛真係我地先明...btw貓貓好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，早幾年我frd隻貓又係病，變到勁瘦，佢火化嗰日我都有去，喊死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f5470dc7e9664ee874c2309c2243902983cb98","tid":1674370,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b15b9dcf27a2a9a9e61674ab27e3d17683b5d2","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf52753c3309df1161431334d19a634ec68e3692","tid":1674370,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9744b89f29554bab4d509508e34211db629626c0","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T22:33:21.000Z","msg":"同你好似，佢又係脾氣好差，佢唔肯食真係無人迫到。雲芝，黑酵母我都有買，但佢食唔夠一半就開始無曬食慾了，所以我都餵唔到。。唉。其實佢好辛苦既話我寧願佢訓住走，唔想佢受咁多苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瘦到皮包骨。btw多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得依加處於人生低谷，好難過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"餵唔到都要諗方法餵吖，我嗰時係用蜜糖溝雲芝蟲草嘅粉（拆開膠囊），撈完當醬查麵包畀佢，後期佢嗰食麵包，鍾意食潔齒骨，我就用潔齒骨「了」啲藥醬畀佢... <br />\n<br />\n嗰時呀女都好瘦好瘦，走嗰時得14.4kg，明明最高峰係21kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人話kakato嘅杞子雞罐罐好香，佢哋鍾意食，你可以試吓<br />\n嗰時我個女鍾意食be my baby嘅罐罐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完醫生，醫生都話做唔到啲咩，打左止痛，拎左開胃藥，返到屋企佢都好累了。可能夜啲再試下餵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢個大pat pat無左，頸啲肉唔見曬，嗰種心痛真係... 唯一係精神還可以，會肯落街。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"如果止痛+開胃<br />\n可能會食到多少少嘢<br />\n爭取時間帶佢去多啲街<br />\n等你地留返啲美好回憶<br />\n絕症狗狗，未必可以醫得好，但延長時間就可以減少主人日後嘅遺憾，加油吖！"},{"pid":"7649a68f67f50bc0ab9676324df9858c32719e1f","tid":1674370,"uid":263932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78721cc5fd926a4e109976d88c00a0eada58bcc1","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6136b6312dde599d579428789ae068ecc7f05af","tid":1674370,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5dc078b56ce983ff1c1bb76bdac84f13eefb410","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"我都想唔洗番工全天候係佢身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一出門我都好不安"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"咁唯有盡力放左工就仆返屋企陪佢啦多d摸下佢錫下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前就係放左學掛住補習 結果咁啱個日補耐左 返到屋企就已經見唔到我隻狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"一諗到將來佢只會存在係我既記憶，我就傷心到死，要好好記得觸摸佢既感覺，佢既氣味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"Virtual hug here <br />\n一個人面對唔容易<br />\n狗狗一定知你好錫佢<br />\n多啲同佢講你有幾愛佢"},{"pid":"0e0e45dc079c9864250e4fe2691e0abbb5e756be","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28f5470