"},{"pid":"a54c09e207dbb2dc4efed9e9c8e8e86c167b58d6","tid":1674370,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"樓主同狗狗都要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95410621602f68a1e687decc022f89b475f009e5","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"好奇怪，佢依加只肯食人食既野，例如唐記排骨肉，譚仔豬潤同雞肉。但無所謂啦，佢肯食就得，因為幾日無咩落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日試下買其他佢食，有無人有相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc08361d8f33bb30f0609a5c0fac91d8a884873","tid":1674370,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔食嘢<br />\n氣喘<br />\n喊<br />\n坐立不安<br />\n都係痛嘅sign<br />\n<br />\n有冇問過醫生可唔可以俾高啲劑量嘅嗎啡？"},{"pid":"c3b6695a30a5c080f38c409054afa48dde262093","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fc08361d8f33bb30f0609a5c0fac91d8a884873","tid":1674370,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔食嘢<br />\n氣喘<br />\n喊<br />\n坐立不安<br />\n都係痛嘅sign<br />\n<br />\n有冇問過醫生可唔可以俾高啲劑量嘅嗎啡？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"尋日有睇醫生打左支止痛針，然後夜晚12點再食止痛藥，但尋晚佢反而成晚好唔舒服，唔訓覺，然後我無再比止痛，so far依加都訓得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗎啡我又無問，如果佢再有痛既表現，就複診問下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e194a9bf2f52e0602d52c1e8dce2584a02f68c7a","tid":1674370,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b6695a30a5c080f38c409054afa48dde262093","tid":1674370,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fc08361d8f33bb30f0609a5c0fac91d8a884873","tid":1674370,"uid":28